		{"id":"text-var2-ad11","type":"text","text":"**Variation 2**\nMessage-Direct: Close-up of a hand tightly gripping a landline phone receiver.","x":2450,"y":80,"width":400,"height":100},
		{"id":"text-var1-ad11","type":"text","text":"**Variation 1**\nPersona Life (Native): Messy desk with invoices and a \"Denied\" letter.","x":2000,"y":80,"width":400,"height":100},
		{"id":"text-ad15","type":"text","text":"# Ad #15 — The Mastermind\n\n\"David, you're building an empire, but you're letting your health crumble.\"\n\nMy buddy Mark said that to me during our monthly business lunch.\n\nI wanted to be angry, but I knew he was right. \n\nI’m 45. I own a small business. I spend every waking hour worrying about my employees and my clients.\n\nBut when it came to my own body, I was failing.\n\nI felt \"heavy.\" I was worrying about my heart. I was worrying about my three kids.\n\nI’d been to my doctor, but my insurance denied the coverage, saying I wasn't \"sick enough\" yet.\n\nI felt like I was stuck in a system that didn't care about my longevity.\n\nI tried the fad diets. I tried the expensive trainers. \n\nI spent a fortune on supplements that did nothing but make me feel nauseous.\n\nThen Mark told me about Elevate.\n\nHe said he’d bypassed the insurance red tape and the pharmacy counter entirely.\n\nI took the quiz on my phone before the bill even came.\n\nThe medical review was 100% online. A licensed provider reviewed my history and created a personalized plan.\n\nEverything I needed was delivered discreetly to my door.\n\nThe transformation started with the mental clarity.\n\nThe \"food noise\"—the constant mental obsession with my next meal—just vanished.\n\nI felt in control for the first time in years.\n\nI felt \"lighter\" on my feet. My energy at the office was higher than it had been in a decade.\n\nLast weekend, I played catch with my kids for three hours and didn't need a single break.\n\nI realized I was spending more on business lunches in a week than this program costs.\n\nNow, my professional care plan is $58 a week. \n\nI used Afterpay to start for $0 down.\n\nDon't wait for a health crisis to take action.\n\nSee if you're eligible for medical support today.\n\n[Link: See if you qualify]","x":1540,"y":3960,"width":400,"height":880},
		{"id":"img-var1-ad15","type":"file","file":"Elevate/00 Assets/T003/David_Ad_15/Var1/variant-1.png","x":2000,"y":3960,"width":399,"height":500},
		{"id":"text-var1-ad15","type":"text","text":"**Variation 1**\nPersona Life (Native): Two coffee cups on a polished wood table, fountain pen.","x":2000,"y":4480,"width":400,"height":100},
		{"id":"img-var2-ad15","type":"file","file":"Elevate/00 Assets/T003/David_Ad_15/Var2/variant-1.png","x":2450,"y":3960,"width":399,"height":500},
		{"id":"text-var1-ad25","type":"text","text":"**Variation 1**\nPersona Life (Native): Desk lamp lighting papers, red pen, tea cup, supplements.","x":4000,"y":4480,"width":400,"height":100},
		{"id":"text-var2-ad25","type":"text","text":"**Variation 2**\nMessage-Direct: Close-up of a discarded supplement bottle in a trash can.","x":4450,"y":4480,"width":400,"height":100},
